couchdb-fractalsql (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release: FractalSQL external query server for Apache CouchDB.
  * Static LuaJIT + cJSON (glibc-only runtime dependency).
  * Supports reset / add_fun / map_doc protocol with per-function emit
    batching.

 -- FractalSQLabs <ops@fractalsqlabs.io>  Sun, 20 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
